            <div class="paragraph col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2"><p>The problem area was explored from both macro - energy industry context and trends - and micro - householder needs - perspectives. This uncovered a variety of key insights, including the suggestion that householders are put off by the high upfront cost of current low-carbon equipment and are confused by the kilowatt hour.</p></div>
